About this hotel

A minutes walk from Alona Beach along the Bohol Sea, this laid-back resort in buildings with thatched roofs is 5 km from the Nova Shell Museum and 22 km Tagbilaran ferry terminal.

Check-in time: 2:00 PM
Check-out time: 11:00 AM

Popular amenities

  • Beach access
  • Air conditioning
  • Airport shuttle

    James Chua3 years ago on Google
    5/5
    The place is a few steps away from Alona Beach. We got the family room which is good for 5 people. The rooms are big and clean, beds are firm, towels are provided. Air con unit is powerful enough to cool the entire room. Really quiet at 
    The place is a few steps away from Alona Beach. We got the family room which is good for 5 people. The rooms are big and clean, beds are firm, towels are provided. Air con unit is powerful enough to cool the entire room. Really quiet at night. A water dispenser is available in the garden so you do not need to buy water. Breakfast not included in the cost. No toiletries are provided. They have a store that sells the basic needs for your stay. The receptionists and attendants are very accommodating. True value for money.

    They offer airconditioned rooms with wall fan, hanged tv with cable, hot and 
    Good for group/family trips they have bunk beds and can accommodate a family of 6 in one room.
    They offer airconditioned rooms with wall fan, hanged tv with cable, hot and cold shower, private toilet, sink, free soap and tissue. The beds are soft and thick with one pillow per single bed. The best part for those who are traveling in budget is that the place have a cooking area with stove and gasul where you can cook what you want and they've also provided utensils, plates, and cups per room. A simple, peaceful and quite place away from the crowd but walking distance from the beach and restaurants.

    Really nice place in Alona and near to the beach! If you looking for a goos, clean and cheap place to stay, dont look further. This place has everything, nice little bungalow with a comfy bed. The shower is good and provides hot water 24/7 (not that you need it in the heat). The ac keeps the room nice and cooled at night!
    The owners are really friendly and help you out with sightseeing and scooter rental! If you are looking for a good place to spend a few days, this is the place!

    About this hotel

    A minutes walk from Alona Beach along the Bohol Sea, this laid-back resort in buildings with thatched roofs is 5 km from the Nova Shell Museum and 22 km Tagbilaran ferry terminal.

    Featuring complimentary Wi-Fi, the colorful, straightforward rooms come with cable TV and porches. Family rooms sleep up to 6 people. The cottages provide minifridges and sitting rooms.

    Theres also a garden offering outdoor seating and hammocks.

    Check-in time: 2:00 PM
    Check-out time: 11:00 AM
